---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Governance Runtime for AI-Generated Code">

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-badge">Zero config &middot; Works instantly &middot; Enterprise ready</div>
    <h1>Governance runtime for<br /><span class="gradient-text">AI-generated code</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      Scan, gate, and trace compliance automatically. No setup needed &mdash;
      auto-detects your project, applies sensible defaults, shows findings inline.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-install">
      <pre><code>npm install -g sentrik</code></pre>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/blog/getting-started-in-5-minutes" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
      <a href="https://maxgerhardson.github.io/sentrik-docs" class="btn btn-outline">Read the Docs</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Terminal Demo -->
<section class="demo">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="terminal">
      <div class="terminal-header">
        <span class="terminal-dot red"></span>
        <span class="terminal-dot yellow"></span>
        <span class="terminal-dot green"></span>
        <span class="terminal-title">Terminal</span>
      </div>
      <div class="terminal-body">
        <div class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt">$</span> npm install -g sentrik</div>
        <div class="terminal-line dim">  sentrik: Binary installed</div>
        <div class="terminal-line">&nbsp;</div>
        <div class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt">$</span> cd my-project && sentrik scan</div>
        <div class="terminal-line dim">  Detected: python, javascript &middot; CI: github &middot; Packs: owasp-top-10</div>
        <div class="terminal-line dim">  Scanning 47 files against 22 rules...</div>
        <div class="terminal-line"><span class="sev-crit">CRITICAL</span> OWASP-A03-005 &middot; src/api.py:42 &middot; eval() executes arbitrary code</div>
        <div class="terminal-line"><span class="sev-high">HIGH</span>     OWASP-A01-001 &middot; src/auth.py:18 &middot; Hardcoded credentials</div>
        <div class="terminal-line"><span class="sev-med">MEDIUM</span>   OWASP-A02-003 &middot; src/app.py:7  &middot; MD5 used for hashing</div>
        <div class="terminal-line dim">  3 findings (1 critical, 1 high, 1 medium)</div>
        <div class="terminal-line">&nbsp;</div>
        <div class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt">$</span> sentrik gate</div>
        <div class="terminal-line"><span class="gate-fail">GATE FAILED</span> &mdash; 2 blocking findings (critical, high)</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="demo-caption">No config files. No wizard. Just scan.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- AI Integration Showcase -->
<section class="mcp-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">AI That Writes Compliant Code</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Your AI agent checks compliance rules <em>before</em> writing code. Not after.</p>

    <div class="showcase-block">
      <div class="showcase-text">
        <h3>&#x1F916; MCP: Compliance During Generation</h3>
        <p>Claude Code, Cursor, and VS Code call sentrik via the Model Context Protocol. The AI asks &ldquo;what rules apply?&rdquo; and writes code that passes the gate on the first try.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="showcase-img">
        <img src="/images/mcp-in-action.png" alt="Claude Code calling sentrik MCP tools" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="showcase-block reverse">
      <div class="showcase-text">
        <h3>&#x1F50D; Dashboard: Fix with AI</h3>
        <p>Click any finding, chat with an LLM, and apply the fix &mdash; all from the browser. Compliance officers triage findings without touching an IDE.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="showcase-img">
        <img src="/images/ai-chat-panel.png" alt="AI chat panel fixing a compliance finding" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="showcase-block">
      <div class="showcase-text">
        <h3>&#x1F4E6; Vulnerable Dependencies? Chat, Understand, Fix.</h3>
        <p>Scan dependencies for known CVEs. Click any vulnerability to chat with AI about the risk, where it&rsquo;s used in your code, and what breaks on upgrade. Then click <strong>Apply Fix</strong> to patch the version &mdash; or run <code>--create-pr</code> to open a pull request.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="showcase-img">
        <img src="/images/vuln-chat-1.png" alt="Vulnerability scan — AI chat about CVE risk" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="showcase-block reverse">
      <div class="showcase-text">
        <h3>&#x1F50D; Understand Before You Upgrade</h3>
        <p>The AI explains what the vulnerability means, which parts of your code are affected, and whether the upgrade introduces breaking changes. Then apply the fix with one click.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="showcase-img">
        <img src="/images/vuln-chat-2.png" alt="AI explains vulnerability impact and fix" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="showcase-block">
      <div class="showcase-text">
        <h3>&#x1F4BB; Dashboard &amp; Compliance Reports</h3>
        <p>Real-time compliance score, severity trends, scan history, and one-click evidence export for auditors. Everything from the CLI is reflected in the dashboard.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="showcase-img">
        <img src="/images/dashboard-overview.png" alt="sentrik dashboard overview" class="screenshot" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Value Props -->
<section class="value-props">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Why sentrik?</h2>
    <div class="props-grid">
      <div class="prop-card">
        <div class="prop-icon">&#x26A1;</div>
        <h3>Zero Config</h3>
        <p>Auto-detects your project type, languages, and CI platform. Works immediately &mdash; no wizard, no setup files, no prompts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prop-card">
        <div class="prop-icon">&#x1F6E1;</div>
        <h3>Enforce Standards Automatically</h3>
        <p>14 pre-built packs covering medical devices, aviation, automotive, fintech, PHP/Laravel, Kotlin/Android, and more. Python, JS, Java, C#, Go, C++, Rust, PHP, Kotlin. Or write your own.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prop-card">
        <div class="prop-icon">&#x26D4;</div>
        <h3>Gate Every PR</h3>
        <p>Block non-compliant code in CI/CD. GitHub Actions, Azure Pipelines, and GitLab CI. PR comments show per-framework compliance summary, file coverage map, and top findings.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prop-card">
        <div class="prop-icon">&#x1F4BB;</div>
        <h3>VS Code &amp; Cursor</h3>
        <p>Install the extension and findings appear inline on save. Auto-initializes, scans in background, status bar shows count. Zero interaction.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prop-card">
        <div class="prop-icon">&#x1F517;</div>
        <h3>Trace Everything</h3>
        <p>Link findings to Azure DevOps, GitHub Issues, or Jira work items. Auto-create, update, and close items on reconcile.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prop-card">
        <div class="prop-icon">&#x1F916;</div>
        <h3>Built for AI Agents</h3>
        <p>Agent context generation, MCP server integration, pre-commit hooks, auto-patching. <code>sentrik audit-mcp</code> scans MCP configs for security risks. Works with Copilot, Cursor, Claude Code, and custom agents.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prop-card">
        <div class="prop-icon">&#x1F4E6;</div>
        <h3>Supply Chain Security</h3>
        <p>SBOM generation (CycloneDX/SPDX), vulnerability scanning against OSV.dev, license compliance with copyleft detection. Auto-remediation with <code>--fix</code> and <code>--create-pr</code>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prop-card">
        <div class="prop-icon">&#x1F916;</div>
        <h3>Works Inside Your AI Agent</h3>
        <p>MCP server integration for Claude Code, Cursor, and VS Code. Your AI agent checks compliance <em>during</em> code generation &mdash; not after. It writes compliant code the first time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prop-card">
        <div class="prop-icon">&#x1F3E2;</div>
        <h3>Security Posture Management</h3>
        <p>ASPM scoring aggregates compliance, vulnerability, trend, and gate data into a single posture score. Multi-repo org dashboard, auditor portal, GRC integration (Drata, Vanta, Secureframe), evidence export, long-term metrics.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Install Options -->
<section class="install-options">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Install in Seconds</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">One command. Downloads a platform-specific binary. No runtime dependencies.</p>
    <div class="install-single">
      <pre><code>npm install -g sentrik</code></pre>
      <p>Downloads a platform binary. No Python, no Docker, no extra dependencies. Works on macOS, Linux, and Windows.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Standards -->
<section class="standards">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Standards Packs</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">12 pre-built regulatory rule sets across 8+ languages. Auto-detected from your README, or enable in one command. Plus SBOM generation, vulnerability tracking, license scanning, and C/C++ semantic analysis.</p>
    <div class="standards-grid">
      <div class="standard-card">
        <h3>IEC 62304</h3>
        <div class="badge" style="background: #7c3aed33; color: #a78bfa;">14 checks &middot; 8 languages</div>
        <p>Medical device software lifecycle. FDA 510(k), EU MDR. Traceability headers, input validation, documentation obligations.</p>
        <code>sentrik add-pack fda-iec-62304</code>
      </div>
      <div class="standard-card">
        <h3>OWASP Top 10</h3>
        <div class="badge" style="background: #ef444433; color: #fca5a5;">22 checks &middot; 8 languages</div>
        <p>Web application security. SQL injection, XSS, auth failures, SSRF. Auto-enabled for every project.</p>
        <code>sentrik add-pack owasp-top-10</code>
      </div>
      <div class="standard-card">
        <h3>SOC2</h3>
        <div class="badge" style="background: #06b6d433; color: #67e8f9;">16 checks &middot; 8 languages</div>
        <p>Trust Services Criteria. Access control, logging, change management. Audit evidence generation.</p>
        <code>sentrik add-pack soc2</code>
      </div>
      <div class="standard-card">
        <h3>HIPAA</h3>
        <div class="badge" style="background: #10b98133; color: #6ee7b7;">15 checks &middot; 8 languages</div>
        <p>Health data privacy and security. PHI handling, encryption requirements, access controls, audit trails for healthcare applications.</p>
        <code>sentrik add-pack hipaa</code>
      </div>
      <div class="standard-card">
        <h3>PCI DSS</h3>
        <div class="badge" style="background: #f59e0b33; color: #fcd34d;">16 checks &middot; 8 languages</div>
        <p>Payment card security. Cardholder data protection, encryption, secure coding, network segmentation for fintech and e-commerce.</p>
        <code>sentrik add-pack pci-dss</code>
      </div>
      <div class="standard-card">
        <h3>ISO 27001</h3>
        <div class="badge" style="background: #3b82f633; color: #93c5fd;">14 checks &middot; 8 languages</div>
        <p>Information security management. Risk assessment controls, data classification, incident response, security policy enforcement.</p>
        <code>sentrik add-pack iso-27001</code>
      </div>
      <div class="standard-card">
        <h3>PHP Security</h3>
        <div class="badge" style="background: #6366f133; color: #a5b4fc;">15 checks &middot; PHP</div>
        <p>PHP and Laravel security. Code injection, SQL injection, XSS, file inclusion, CSRF, mass assignment, session fixation.</p>
        <code>sentrik add-pack php-security</code>
      </div>
      <div class="standard-card">
        <h3>Kotlin Security</h3>
        <div class="badge" style="background: #8b5cf633; color: #c4b5fd;">13 checks &middot; Kotlin</div>
        <p>Kotlin, Android, and Spring Boot security. SQL injection, WebView exploits, insecure crypto, exported components, command injection.</p>
        <code>sentrik add-pack kotlin-security</code>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="cta">
  <div class="container cta-inner">
    <h2>Ready to govern your AI-generated code?</h2>
    <pre><code>npm install -g sentrik && sentrik scan</code></pre>
    <div class="cta-actions">
      <a href="/blog/getting-started-in-5-minutes" class="btn btn-primary">Read the Quickstart</a>
      <a href="/pricing" class="btn btn-outline">View Pricing</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Base>

<style>
  .hero { padding: 8rem 0 4rem; text-align: center; }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
  .hero h1 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-light), var(--color-accent));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .hero-install {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .hero-install pre {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }
  .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; }

  .screenshot { width: 100%; max-width: 900px; margin: 2rem auto; display: block; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); }

  .demo { padding: 2rem 0 3rem; }
  .terminal {
    max-width: 750px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }
  .terminal-header {
    background: #2d2640;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .terminal-dot { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; }
  .terminal-dot.red { background: #ff5f57; }
  .terminal-dot.yellow { background: #ffbd2e; }
  .terminal-dot.green { background: #28c840; }
  .terminal-title { margin-left: 0.5rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.85rem; }
  .terminal-body {
    background: #1a1428;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .terminal-line { white-space: pre; }
  .terminal-line.dim { color: var(--color-text-muted); }
  .prompt { color: var(--color-success); }
  .sev-crit { color: #ef4444; font-weight: 600; }
  .sev-high { color: #f97316; font-weight: 600; }
  .sev-med { color: #f59e0b; font-weight: 600; }
  .gate-fail { color: #ef4444; font-weight: 700; }
  .demo-caption {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .section-title { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .section-sub { text-align: center; color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; }

  .value-props { background: var(--color-bg-alt); }
  .props-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 2rem; }
  .prop-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  .prop-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .prop-card h3 { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; font-size: 1.2rem; }
  .prop-card p { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; }

  /* AI Showcase Section */
  .mcp-section { padding: 5rem 0; background: var(--color-bg-alt); }
  .showcase-block { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr; gap: 40px; align-items: center; margin: 3rem 0; }
  .showcase-block.reverse { grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; }
  .showcase-block.reverse .showcase-text { order: 2; }
  .showcase-block.reverse .showcase-img { order: 1; }
  .showcase-text h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .showcase-text p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.6; }
  .showcase-img .screenshot { margin: 0; max-width: 100%; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .showcase-block, .showcase-block.reverse { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .showcase-block.reverse .showcase-text, .showcase-block.reverse .showcase-img { order: unset; }
  }
  .mcp-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin: 2rem 0; }
  .mcp-card { background: var(--color-bg); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; }
  .mcp-card h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .mcp-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .mcp-card.mcp-highlight { border-color: #7c3aed; box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px #7c3aed30; }
  .mcp-code { background: #1a1a2e; color: #e0e0e8; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin: 0; overflow-x: auto; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .mcp-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .install-options { padding: 5rem 0; }
  .install-single {
    max-width: 550px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .install-single pre {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }
  .install-single p { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; }

  .standards-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 2rem; }
  .standard-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }
  .standard-card h3 { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .standard-card .badge { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .standard-card p { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .standard-card code { font-size: 0.85rem; }

  .cta { text-align: center; background: var(--color-bg-alt); }
  .cta h2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .cta pre { display: inline-block; padding: 0.75rem 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1rem; }
  .cta-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .props-grid, .standards-grid, .install-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero { padding: 5rem 0 3rem; }
    .hero-actions, .cta-actions { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
    .terminal-body { overflow-x: auto; }
    .terminal-line { white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.75rem; }
    .hero-install pre, .install-single pre, .cta pre { font-size: 0.85rem; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; max-width: 100%; }
    .standard-card code { word-break: break-all; font-size: 0.75rem; }
  }
</style>
